title: #AskGaryVee 237 | Eating Shit for 24 Months, Doing What You Love & Monetizing Your Strengths
description: Another version of the call-in shooooooooww! This one is short, sweet, and POWERFUL. I'm super excited about this format because it allows me to develop real context with the questions and the people asking them. I get a feel for their energy, we can elaborate and discuss more detail, and all in all it's just a much better cadence. Let me know what you think of this !!
